# =============================================================================
# live2d-fork .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Excludes heavy/proprietary model assets on non-canonical paths. Source code,
# configs, and scripts are committed. To use the widget, supply your own Live2D
# model files at vampire/vampire_vts/<your-model>/.
#
# 2026-06-12 policy change: A1 (full static mirror for Cloudflare Pages)
# The vampire/vampire_vts/ tree is now FULLY tracked in git (including the
# 7 MB .moc3 binary) so Cloudflare Pages can serve the complete model from
# BAZOOKA-free static infrastructure. This matches the upstream
# YuriCrystal/ai-avatar-bot repo's posture.
#
# Verification: widget.html line 1030 calls `Live2DModel.from(MODEL_URL)`,
# which requires the .moc3 binary (mesh data) + .model3.json (metadata).
# The 4 .2048 texture PNGs are the actual visual assets. Without all of
# these, the model cannot be rendered at all.
#
# Consumers running their own model should:
#   1. Replace `vampire/vampire_vts/` with their own assets
#   2. Update `vampire.txt` (license/attribution)
#   3. Re-run `scripts/Verify_Vampire_Model.py` to sanity-check params

# --- Local-only copies of model on different paths (not canonical) ---
backend/static/live2d/
frontend/live2d/    # mirror copies of model — not for redistribution
frontend/live2d/**/*.moc3
frontend/live2d/**/*.png
frontend/live2d/**/*.physics3.json
frontend/live2d/**/texture_*
scripts/vampire/

# --- Source archives (development reference only) ---
*.zip

# --- Build output (regenerate via `python build_pages_dist.py`) ---
dist-pages/

scripts/vampire/

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/

# --- Node / front-end ---
node_modules/
.npm
.yarn
dist/
build/
*.log

# --- IDE / OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Local env / secrets ---
.env
.env.local
*.local

# --- Runtime / test artifacts ---
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.backup
scripts/result.txt
scripts/vampire_param_ids.txt
scripts/zip_*.txt

# --- CSP violation reports (runtime audit logs; never commit) ---
backend/logs/
backend/logs/*.jsonl
backend/logs/*.old

# --- FastAPI stdout/stderr logs ---
backend/stdout.log
backend/stderr.log
